msgid "To see how read / write connections should be configured, let's look at this example:"
msgstr "要瞭解如何設定讀、寫連線，來看看這個範例："

#: ./docs/8.x/database.md:77
#: ./docs/9.x/database.md:84
#: ./docs/10.x/database.md:84
